Adding a Zone to a Card Layout

Add cards to a zone or nest card layouts inside a zone to arrange cards into sections.

To add a zone to a card layout:

Click App Launcher, click Vlocity Cards, and click a version of a card layout to open the Card Designer.
Select a template with zones.
Click the black arrow in the Zones pane to expand it, and click the black arrow of a zone to expand.
Edit the zone Label if needed.
Add a card to the zone or add another card layout inside.

Adding a Card Layout to a Zone
